c;">5.15% interest</a>. If you have a billion dollars of crypto deposits, y=
ou can make $51.5 million a year on them just by parking them at the Fed, w=
ith absolutely on interest-rate or liquidity risk. In 2021, you couldn=E2=
=80=99t get that much interest <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusine=
